\c 13
\s Areka inobviswa paKiriati-Jearimi ndokuiswa kuna Obhedhi-Edhomu
\p
\v 1 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakarangana nemisoro yezvuru neyemazana nemutungamiriri umwe neumwe.
\v 2 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakati kuungano yose yaIsraeri: Kana zvakanaka kwamuri, uye zvichibva kuna Jehovha Mwari wedu, ngatibude titume kuhama dzedu dzakasara munyika yose yaIsraeri, nekuvapristi nevaRevhi vanavo mumaguta, mumafuro avo, kuti vaungane kwatiri.
\v 3 Tigodzosera areka yaMwari wedu kwatiri, nokuti hatina kuitsvaka pamazuva aSauro.
\v 4 Ungano yose ndokuti kuitwe saizvozvo; nokuti chinhu chaiva chakarurama pameso evanhu vose.
\v 5 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakaunganidza Israeri wose, kubva paShihori rweEgipita, kusvika pakupinda paHamati, kuuisa areka yaMwari kubva paKiriati-Jearimi.
\v 6 Dhavhidhi naIsraeri wose ndokukwira kuBhahara, kuKiriati-Jearimi riri muJudha, kukwidza kubvapo areka yaMwari Jehovha, agere \add pa\add*makerubhi, panodanwa zita.
\v 7 Zvino vakatakura areka yaMwari mungoro itsva, kubva muimba yaAbhinadhabhu; uye Uza naAhio vakachaira ngoro.
\v 8 Dhavhidhi naIsraeri wose ndokutamba pamberi paMwari nesimba rose, uye nenziyo, uye nembira, uye nemitengeranwa, uye nengoma, uye nemakandira, uye nehwamanda.
\p
\v 9 Pavakasvika paburiro raKidhoni, Uza wakatandavadza ruoko rwake kubata areka, nokuti nzombe dzaigumburwa.
\v 10 Kutsamwa kwaJehovha ndokupfutira Uza, ndokumurova, nokuti wakatandavadzira ruoko rwake kuareka; ndokufirapo pamberi paMwari.
\v 11 Dhavhidhi ndokutsamwa nokuti Jehovha wakapaza \add kuti\add* apazire Uza; ndokutumidza nzvimbo iyo Perezi-Uza, kusvika zuva rino.
\v 12 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakatya Mwari nezuva iro, achiti: Ndingauisa sei areka yaMwari kwandiri?
\v 13 Naizvozvo Dhavhidhi haana kuuisa areka kwaari, kuguta raDhavhidhi, asi akaitsausira kumba kwaObhedhi-Edhomu muGiti.
\v 14 Areka yaMwari ndokugara kune veimba yaObhedhi-Edhomu muimba yake mwedzi mitatu; Jehovha ndokuropafadza imba yaObhedhi-Edhomu nezvose zvaaiva nazvo.